content:
Hi everyone,

Apologies if this isn't the right stream for this, but if you are in Chicago today for KubeCon this week, we would love to have you stop by the WebAssembly Social tonight (November 5), at 8pm. Hosted by several of the WebAssembly Community Meetup groups, this is an informal event to just hang out, chat, and network, just a short walk from the convention center (McCormick Place West). Drinks and snacks will be provided.

details/signup: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/wasm-social-tickets-736290965097

Hope to see you there!

Wasm_Social_Sign.png

Wasm Social
Wasm Community Social -- A happy hour/social hosted by the Wasm Community Meetup Groups!
